      "span_text": "To perform the band shifting from an input wavelength λ i to a target wavelength λ t , the IOPs are calculated at these two wavelengths using the spectral shape assumed in the QAA for b bp and a dg , and that given by Bricaud et al.  for a ph (since the QAA does not make assumptions on the spectral shape of a ph , except for the ratio of a ph at two wavelengths in the blue).",
